data.description: Charming Ranch-Style Home sits on a generous quarter-acre property, offering a stair-free living experience. With four bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and a well-appointed kitchen featuring solid Maple cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances, it's a comfortable and stylish residence. Recent updates in 2023 include a new roof for both the main house and garage, fresh siding, modern gutters, newly installed soffits, and upgraded flooring throughout. The property also boasts a new garage window and updated window treatments. In 2014, extensive improvements were made, including new windows, plumbing, electrical systems, and HVAC. This home is move-in ready, requiring only unpacking. FHA and VA buyers are welcome, offering accessibility and convenience for all. With recent upgrades and exceptional condition, it's an opportunity not to be missed.
